summary: Yet another mountain retexture comes to the skyrim community. With normal and parallax maps, this mountain retexture will hopefully stand out above the rest.
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to my first skyrim mod. This is not my first mod that I have ever made though. I have made many mods for Team Fortress 2 and posted them on Gamebanana. I posted a few of them here on Nexus such as Complete HD Retexture, Improved Blueprints, HD Snow, etc.

I hope you enjoy this mod for skyrim. I am currently working on a landscape overhaul which will take quite a bit longer than this did. Please leave a comment and endorse!
author: Megamawman
